[[File:Lvl-1 Enchant icon (mobile).png|left]]
'''Lvl-1 Enchant''' is a [[utility spell]] in the [[standard spellbook]], requiring level 7 [[Magic]] to cast. The spell enchants [[sapphire]] and [[opal]] items, primarily [[jewellery]], granting 17.5 Magic experience when doing so.

This spell can be transferred to a [[Enchant sapphire or opal|magic tablet]] by bringing the required runes and a piece of [[soft clay]] to a [[lectern]] in the [[study]] of a [[player-owned house]], granting the same experience as casting the spell.

